* PREREQUISITES
*
* MySQL
* Kannel

INSTALLATION
* Checkout project
* Try virtualenv.py --relocatable env/
* If it doesn't work, recreate virtualenv 
	rm -rf env/
	virtualenv.py  env/
	env/bin/pip -r requirements.txt

* Configuration
	Don't forget to put correct values to IPADDR and PORT. These are used to craft the DLR URL